<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">شِعْرًا:</span> ... فَلا تَرْجُ إِلا اللهِ فِي كُلِّ حَادِثٍ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>فَأَلْقِ إليه بَثَّ شَكْوَاكَ تُحْمَدُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>لَهُ المَلْكُ بِالأَكْوَانِ لا بِمُؤازِرِنْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَلا بَنَصِيرٍ فِي الدِّفَاعِ لِمُعْتَدِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>قَرِيبُ وَلَكِنَ بِالذُّنُوبَ تَبَاعَدَتْ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>مَسَائِلُنَا عَنْ رَوْضِ إِحْسَانِهِ النَّدِي<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَقُمْ قَارِعًا لِلْبَابِ وَالنَّابِ نَادِمًا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>عَلَى مَا جَرَى وَارْفَعْ دُعَاءَكَ يَصْعَدِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَقُمْ سَائِلاً وَالدَّمْعُ فِي الخَدِّ سَائِلٌ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>تَجِدْ مَا تَشَا مِنْ لُطْفِهِ وَكَأنْ قَدِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَقُمْ زُلَفًا فِي اللَّيْلِ إِنْ نَشَرَ الدُّجَى<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>جَنَاحَ غُدَافٍ يُلْبِسُ الكَوْنَ عَنْ يَدِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَرُدَّ ظَلامَ اللَّيْلِ بِالذِّكْرِ مُشْرِقًا<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>فَقَدْ فَازَ مَنْ بِالذِّكْرِ يَهْدِي وَيَهْتَدِي<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَأَمَّا بَنُو الدُّنْيَا فَلا تَرْجُ نَفْعَهُمْ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>فَلا مُنْجِدٌ فِيهِمْ يُرَجَّى لِمُجْتَدِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>فَإِنِّي تَتَبَّعْتُ الأَنَاَم فَلَمْ أَجِدْ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>سِوَى شَامِتٍ أَوْ حَاسِدٍ أو مُفَنِّدِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَقَدْ رَضَعُوا ثَدْيَ المَهَابَةِ كُلُّهُمْ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَكُلٌ بِذَيْلِ الذُّلِّ أَصْبِحَ مُرْتَدِ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>فلم أَرَ أَرْمَى إَلا بِالسِّهَامِ مِن الدُّعَا<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>إَلَى مَقْتَلِ الأَعْدَاءِ مِنْ قَوْسِ مِذْوَد ... &gt;?<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>